snippet: The Talea Ensemble performed works by the modern composers Pierluigi Billone, Bernhard Gander and Olga Neuwirth as part of the Vienna: City of Dreams festival.
abstract: Steve Smith reviews performance by Talea Ensemble at Austrian Cultural Forum as part of Carnegie Hall's Vienna: City of Dreams festival.
lead_paragraph: The Talea Ensemble performed works by the modern composers Pierluigi Billone, Bernhard Gander and Olga Neuwirth as part of the Vienna: City of Dreams festival.

headline.seo: Talea Ensemble Performs in Vienna: City of Dreams Festival
